Package: QuantMgmt
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative Management Tools for Machine Learning
Version: 0.5.0
Author: yufeng.lai
Maintainer: yufeng.lai <yufeng.lai@example.com>
Authors@R: person("yufeng.lai", email = "yufeng.lai@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of tools for automated machine learning model tuning,
    prediction, and evaluation. Provides functions for hyperparameter tuning of
    classification algorithms, performance evaluation, and ensemble predictions.
    Supports both local mlr3 and distributed Spark ML backends.
